{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9a753cddf1","title":"对关于在东北地区部署中苏空军作战部队报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"03c35a7b36","index":0,"year":1950,"month":7,"day":18,"articleId":"9a753cddf1"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"365462d356","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9a753cddf1","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中国人民解放军空军司令员刘亚楼、副司令员常乾坤、副政治委员兼政治部主任吴法宪、副政治委员王和参谋长王秉章1950年7月18日报告的批语。"},{"id":"e0255b4888","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9a753cddf1","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘亚楼、常乾坤等的报告说：根据东北现有机场状况并经过与顾问同志商讨结果，对于我空军第四混成旅及苏联即将派来的一个空军喷气式驱逐机师之部署，作如下之建议：我第四混成旅在南京、徐州地区编组完成后，即转移到东北地区：以两个驱逐团及混成旅部驻安东，一个轰炸团驻四平或海龙。苏联来的一个喷气式驱逐师，则准备以师部及两个团驻鞍山，一个团驻辽阳。这样六个空军团配置在沈阳周围。上述各地机场、房屋、道路，据我们派人实地侦察，基本上都可利用现有的。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f5da005c40","type":"title","text":"对关于在东北地区部署中苏空军作战部队报告的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9a753cddf1"},{"id":"365462d356","type":"subtitle","text":"同意。]","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9a753cddf1"},{"id":"e0255b4888","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9a753cddf1"},{"id":"d7d0e6e1d1","type":"paragraph","text":"七月十八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9a753cddf1"}],"page":{"id":"c6f4befd1b","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9a753cddf1","start":539,"end":539}}}},"__N_SSG":true}